('9538c278-5c2e-573a-ba54-b63bc364f333', 'ec13042a-727a-4875-a281-5d1e2bacc420', 'You should ___ your bad habits.', '你應該改變你的壞習慣。', 'change', 'drink', 'sing', 'sleep', 'change (v.) 表示改變', 'change (v.) 改變 → 改變習慣要 change', '2026-07-07 03:09:56', '2026-07-07 03:09:56'),
('f9453af1-c07a-535d-8d15-2a4fe7e4a0cb', '4ff84157-82c3-4136-9010-2514b31033ff', 'Tim is a ___ student; he always studies hard and completes his homework on time.', 'Tim 是個 ___ 的學生；他總是努力學習並準時完成作業。', 'diligent', 'careless', 'greedy', 'noisy', '源自拉丁語 diligere，原意為「挑選、喜愛」，引申為因為對事情有熱忱而認真、勤勉地去做。', '想像一個勤奮的人會「低(di)」頭「勤(li)」奮地工作 → diligent。', '2026-07-07 04:32:32', '2026-07-07 04:32:32'),
('5c71311e-f1db-5145-948e-9185a58b12b7', '5de28828-06f8-48ca-a690-14250196a190', 'Please go ___ and help your mother with the housework.', '請下樓去幫妳媽媽做家事。', 'downstairs', 'outside', 'away', 'nearby', 'down (向下) + stairs (樓梯) → downstairs (樓下/樓下的)', 'down (向下) + stairs (樓梯) → 想像走下樓梯的動作 → downstairs (樓下)', '2026-07-07 05:26:10', '2026-07-07 05:26:10'),
